General.Name: Kingsrose Mining Ltd
General.Description: Kingsrose Mining Limited operates as an exploration company in Norway, Finland, and Indonesia. It explores for PGE-nickel-copper, gold, and silver properties. The company holds a 100% interest in the Penikat Project located in western Finland and the Porsanger project in Norway. It also holds 85% interest in the Way Linggo project located in South Sumatra, Indonesia. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
